{
    "title": "Quando o Amor Acontece",
    "artist": "João Bosco",
    "composer": "João Bosco / Abel Silva",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7M(9)\">A7M(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am9\">Am9</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9/11+)\">D7(9/11+)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/G#\">E/G#</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#m7\">C#m7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(2)\">B7(2)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9-)\">B7(9-)</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E9\">E9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Coração sem perdão, diga fale por mim  </span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m/B\">G#m/B</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gº\">Gº</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quem roubou toda a minha alegria  </span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(2)\">B7(2)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(2)\">B7(2)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O amor me pegou, me pegou pra valer</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(2)\">B7(2)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É a dor do querer, muda o tempo e a maré  </span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(2)\">B7(2)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9-)\">B7(9-)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E9\">E9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vendaval sob o mar azul</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E9\">E9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tantas vezes chorei, quase me desesperei  </span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m/B\">G#m/B</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gº\">Gº</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E jurei nunca mais seus carinhos  </span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(2)\">B7(2)</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(2)\">B7(2)</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ninguém tira do amor, ninguém tira, pois é  </span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(2)\">B7(2)</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(2)\">B7(2)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9-)\">B7(9-)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nem doutor nem pajé, o que queima e seduz, enlouquece  </span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E9\">E9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O veneno da mulher  </span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm11\">Bm11</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7(9-/13)\">E7(9-/13)</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7M(9)\">A7M(9)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am9\">Am9</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9/11+)\">D7(9/11+)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O amor quando acontece a gente esquece logo que sofreu um dia, ilusão  </span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/G#\">E/G#</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#m7\">C#m7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(2)\">B7(2)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9-)\">B7(9-)</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E9\">E9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O meu coração marcado tinha um nome tatuado que ainda doía, pulsava só na solidão  </span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm11\">Bm11</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7(9-/13)\">E7(9-/13)</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7M(9)\">A7M(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am9\">Am9</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9/11+)\">D7(9/11+)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O amor quando acontece a gente esquece logo que sofreu um dia, esquece sim  </span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/G#\">E/G#</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#m7\">C#m7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7\">F#m7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quem mandou chegar tão perto se era certo um outro engano,  coração cigano  </span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(2)\">B7(2)</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9-)\">B7(9-)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E9\">E9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E agora eu choro assim  </span>\n\n[Final] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M/E\">C7M/E</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#º/C\">F#º/C</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7(9-)\">B7(9-)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E9\">E9</span>\n",
